{% macro render_naming_conventions(language) -%}
### Naming Conventions

{% if language == 'python' -%}
| Element | Convention | Example |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| Files | snake_case | `user_service.py` |
| Variables | snake_case | `user_count`, `is_active` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE (in config) | Use pydantic-settings instead |
| Classes/Types | PascalCase | `UserService`, `LoginRequest` |
| Functions | snake_case | `get_user_by_id()` |
| Methods | snake_case | `user.validate_email()` |
| Private methods | _snake_case | `_internal_method()` |
| Dunder methods | __snake_case__ | `__init__()`, `__str__()` |
| Database tables | snake_case | `user_accounts`, `order_items` |
| Environment vars | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `DATABASE_URL`, `API_KEY` |
| Module names | snake_case | `auth.py`, `user_service.py` |
| Package names | snake_case | `src/auth/`, `src/models/` |

